snippet.title: Process of Elimination - Story Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/process-of-elimination/                        

14 detectives have gathered to stop a heinous killer at large. But how do they know who to trust when the killer they seek could be any one of them? The game is afoot in Process of Elimination!

Coming April 11, 2023 to Nintendo Switch and PS4!

#ProcessofElimination
